<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Two Column Blog Layout</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      margin: 0;
      background: #f5f5f5;
    }

    header {
      background: #333;
      color: white;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 15px;
    }

    .container {
      display: flex;
      gap: 20px;
      padding: 20px;
    }

    .main {
      flex: 2;
      background: white;
      padding: 15px;
      border-radius: 8px;
    }

    .sidebar {
      flex: 1;
      background: white;
      padding: 15px;
      border-radius: 8px;
    }

    footer {
      background: #333;
      color: white;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 10px;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }

    /* Media Query for small screens */
    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      .container {
        flex-direction: column;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <header>
    <h1>My Two-Column Blog</h1>
  </header>

  <div class="container">
    <div class="main">
      <h2>Main Content</h2>
      <p>This is where your main blog posts will appear. You can add multiple paragraphs, images, or links here.</p>
      <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Integer et sem non elit aliquet volutpat.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="sidebar">
      <h2>Sidebar</h2>
      <p>This is your sidebar section. You can add categories, recent posts, or advertisements here.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <footer>
    <p>&copy; 2025 My Blog</p>
  </footer>

</body>
</html>
